Alcoa - Wikipedia






















 






Alcoa

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the company. For the town, see Alcoa, Tennessee. For the river, see Alcoa River. For other uses, see Alcoa (disambiguation).

Alcoa Corp.





Type

Public


Traded as



NYSE: AA





Industry
